WEBVTT

00:02.184 --> 00:05.119
Optimus: And it was written
in the covenant of Primus

00:05.121 --> 00:11.025
that when the 47 spheres align,
a perpetual conflict will culminate

00:11.027 --> 00:18.066
upon a world forged from chaos,
and the weak shall perish

00:18.068 --> 00:21.669
in the shadow
of a rising darkness.

00:21.671 --> 00:23.805
No skies raining fire?

00:23.807 --> 00:25.540
Goes without saying.

00:25.542 --> 00:27.909
It is a doom prophecy, after all.

00:27.911 --> 00:29.944
I say it's a load of hooey.

00:29.946 --> 00:33.147
I'd always assumed the ancients
were referring to our home planet,

00:33.149 --> 00:36.050
but being that Cybertron
has been dark for eons...

00:36.052 --> 00:39.153
Optimus: And considering
what has befallen this planet

00:39.155 --> 00:41.189
since Megatron's arrival here...

00:41.191 --> 00:42.957
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

00:42.959 --> 00:45.226
We've known about
these superstitions for ages

00:45.228 --> 00:47.128
and never gave them
a second thought.

00:47.130 --> 00:48.896
Why all the ominous
rumblings now?

00:48.898 --> 00:53.000
Because the planetary alignment
to which the prophecy refers

00:53.002 --> 00:54.769
is nearly upon us.

00:54.771 --> 00:59.741
And it would seem
its end point...Is earth.

00:59.743 --> 01:03.911
Uh...Crazy coincidence,
heh, r-right?

01:03.913 --> 01:06.047
How long are we talking?

01:06.049 --> 01:08.649
A few days at most.

01:10.352 --> 01:13.221
However unsettling
this revelation may be,

01:13.223 --> 01:16.491
I am more concerned about those
who might believe

01:16.493 --> 01:20.795
That the prophecy
speaks to them alone.

01:20.797 --> 01:23.865
I did not seek out
the blood of Unicron

01:23.867 --> 01:26.401
To simply keep my spark aflame,

01:26.403 --> 01:29.871
but to rule undead armies
and conquer worlds,

01:29.873 --> 01:31.639
and to accomplish that,

01:31.641 --> 01:34.375
I require more
than this mere sliver

01:34.377 --> 01:36.177
which lies within me.

01:36.179 --> 01:40.014
So, where is my Dark Energon?!

01:40.016 --> 01:41.983
Out there, lord Megatron,

01:41.985 --> 01:44.685
just waiting for you
to reach out and pluck it.

01:46.021 --> 01:48.623
But you shouldn't
push yourself so hard.

01:48.625 --> 01:51.259
You've had setbacks.
You were in stasis.

01:51.261 --> 01:52.427
Oh!

01:52.429 --> 01:55.563
Precisely why I must
make up for lost time!

01:55.565 --> 01:58.166
I can see the future vividly,

01:58.168 --> 02:00.868
but I must ensure its outcome,

02:00.870 --> 02:06.574
for I am the rising darkness
of which the prophecy speaks!

